  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will compare two forms of advice regarding physical activity for patients&#xD;
      hospitalized with cirrhosis that are preparing for leaving the hospital. One arm consists of&#xD;
      current standard of care: simple oral advice on exercise. One arm instead gives patients a&#xD;
      structured but simple paper template on physical activity.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
